divs: Sighting DetailsWas able to view object in the last few minutes prior to sunset against a cloudy sky. Undefined blimp like shape that stood out starkly against a darkening sky. No lights or sound. Object remained visible until the sky darkened at about 8:25 p.m. Trained meteorologist here and this left goosebumps. Too dark for photography.
